Class CustomerDTO

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public final class CustomerDTO
extends UserDTO
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class follows the Data Transfert Object design pattern. It is a client view of a Customer. This class only transfers data from a distant service to a client.
